text: Félix Schnyder (5 March 1910 – 8 November 1992) was a Swiss lawyer and diplomat. He was Chairman of UNICEF in 1960 and United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees from 1960 to 1965.Felix Schnyder, United Nations High Commissioner for Refugees ==References== Category:1910 births Category:1992 deaths Category:Swiss politicians Category:Swiss lawyers Category:European diplomats Category:United Nations High Commissioners for Refugees Category:People from the canton of Bern
